I’m doing this project for school however I chose this because I’ve always been interested in game design and this is a subcategory of designing a game. I’ve played games since I was about 8 or 9 years old, being 20 that means I’ve spent most of my life playing games, I became vastly into them, form simple means of enjoyment to being interested in how they were made and what tricks creators used to make a game run better while looking the same. I was fascinated. I got into VR relatively recently thanks to its blowing up in popularity and my PS4 coming out with its own VR system, currently I am building a PC that has better components to run a better VR system but I’ve put in a decent few hours with my VR headset to have a firsthand experience and have been interests in gaming as a whole as well.
